Left Joystick:
Left and right controls servo 1 left and right
 - This moves the arm left and right
Up and Down controls servo 2 forward and backward
 - This moves the first arm servo forward or backward
 
 Right Joystick:
 Up and Down Control servo 3 forward and backward
  - This moves the second arm servo forward or backward
 
 Triggers:
 Right shoulder controls claw open (servo 4)
 Left shoulder controls claw close
 
X and B (Square and Circle on PS4):
- B moves sample storage clockwise (servo 5)
- X moves sample storage ccw
 
 
